NOMOROTHAT tracked the pace in the middle of the pack from the two path then faded throughout the far turn and never fired in the stretch. EXPECT LAVENDER was unhurried early then trailed behind the field and was no factor. There was a STEWARDS INQUIRY in regards to the stretch drive.
